The Users will be redirected to Secure Access Washington(SAW) for Authentication,  when they choose Washington FHIR Server from any third party application. SAW will post back a SAML assertion to Washington's SMART on FHIR once the user is authenticated through SAW. SMART on FHIR will create/update the User Profile, obtain Authorization and Consent from the user, validate the patient and associate the Patient ID with Login ID.
